                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He then</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">
to a former conviction of a like offence, in October, 1857, when he was sentenced to four years' penal servitude; it was further stated that a desperate attempt to rescue him was made as he entered Newgate
